{"tid":790661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，麥當勞嗰位老豆買唔到包跟住大吵大鬧係人之常情","createTime":"2018-08-23T07:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T17:19:06.000Z","uid":123613,"like":43,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9def973e13534404fd9a6e8dfbe5ad4629876ca7","tid":790661,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"可能連登仔未做過老豆或者未供過樓唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將心比己，如果你係個老豆，你比上司屌完，又要OT到夜一夜先走得，你心情會點？<br />\n<br />\n點解要為10蚊嘈？如果你供緊樓，啲錢自然要慳住咁洗，買多少少錢都要諗過度過<br />\n<br />\n一做老豆，為咗個女，連自己僅餘的私人時間都冇埋，返到屋企見個女咁肚餓，幾夜都要仆落去買，加上你又要供樓又要OT又要養老婆，壓力係點可想而知<br />\n<br />\n利申，非片中嗰位老豆，只係香港地類似咁燥嘅老豆老母真係見唔少"},{"pid":"664dce14e8859a9c3f712d6d30cfd53d4250cef9","tid":790661,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77655ca52f90b5d847d6adfb6cecc53d5ecfa7d","tid":790661,"uid":29270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"生活咁多壓力<br />\n食個M記都要俾人呃俾人撚<br />\n<br />\n梗係燥啦"},{"pid":"ce6087e520632b43e9ce286d9f79b634d28d9162","tid":790661,"uid":44412,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"洗撚咁多藉口咩<br />\n今次麥當勞係抵屌"},{"pid":"b42bdf9b9c4a4e39e608e0f508f1f201406793c3","tid":790661,"uid":21861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"我諗佢屌m記不公義多過個少少錢"},{"pid":"6330a87d7514c39c385b76b2120054c645bf2ca3","tid":790661,"uid":33481,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b42bdf9b9c4a4e39e608e0f508f1f201406793c3","tid":790661,"uid":21861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"我諗佢屌m記不公義多過個少少錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"香港賤民只會focus係少少錢 唔會理公義問題"},{"pid":"ebb50a3773f100e38738d3f1269f2f340c0088ef","tid":790661,"uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"